Canterbury Carpet Cleaning Case Study
Milestone 1: Analysis of Scope & Business Case

Functions and Features Wish List:
Handling accounting, billing, inventory, and vehicle management in one place
Routing and forecasting in same place

Carpet_PRO system:
Employee assigned to vehicle and given an initial schedule with jobs for the day as well as GPS instructions
Schedule subject to change throughout day requiring ability to update live
Terminal can be updated by driver to show job completion before directing to next job

Customer Relationship Management System or other single place to handle customer data
Website able to gather whether service is available in area identified by user


